defaultWhen I 
defaultdecided to launch
default work to construct CONTEST in October 2002 we 
defaultwere unsure
default what should be the 
defaultultimate 
defaultaim to which all those involved in 
defaultthe UK 
defaultcounter-terrorism
default effort
default, directly and indirectly, should bend their ef
defaultforts.  For the United States, 
defaultsuffering from the aftermath of 9/11
default,
