defaultalter the aim
default.
default  
default&#xa0;
defaultThe success of Pursue (and equivalent efforts by allies 
defaultand partners overseas) has been
default 
defaultnot 
defaultonly in disrupting networks in the UK and their links overseas (including a significant number of major plots that have been well reported
default in the media
default), but also making it much harder 
defaultfor violent jihadists 
defaultto operate in the UK without detection.  The effect has, as the Committee
default has recognised, been a
default shift 
defaultin the UK 
defaultfrom large-scale plots that require long term planning, organisation (including support from trained jihadists overseas) and finance 
defaultto smaller, cruder local attacks.  
default 
default&#xa0;
defaultIt should be b
defaultorne in mind, however, that such a
default 
defaultmutation
default 
defaultin the threat 
defaultcould quickly reverse if the pressure was taken off, and if jihadists were to regain the initiativ
defaulte in havens overseas such as 
defaultYemen
